	   Modified Files:
		  XMLSchema.py -- added a "getItemTrace" method to
	  XMLSchemaComponent
		     Base class to produce a node trace.  Added a bunch of
	  "tag"
		     class variables for identifying what an instance
	  represents,
		     and removed a bunch of unused code.


