	  ws-address, ws-resourcepolicy, etc)

		  WSDLTools.py -- added functionality for getting
	  WS-ResourceProperties and
		     ws-Address information out of WSDL.  Ran all unittests
	  and passed.


	  ----------------------------------------------------------------------

